{"word":"G2027 - ἐποκέλλω - epokéllō - ep-ok-el'-lo - Run aground","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐποκέλλω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">epokéllō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ep-ok-el'-lo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Run aground</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - தட்டவை"},{"paragraph":"to drive upon, strike against"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1909 - ἐπί - epí - ep-ee'/1909\">G1909</a> and <b>&#x03BF;&#x0313;&#x03BA;&#x03B5;&#x0301;&#x03BB;&#x03BB;&#x03C9;</b> <b>okello&#x0304;</b> (to <i>urge</i>); to <i>drive upon</i> the shore, that is, to <i>beach</i> a vessel: - run aground.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}